title: Disney's Princess Bedtime Story Elsa as Little Red Riding Hood

json.text: Today I will tell you a story, A story about a little girl Elsa, who wanted
to give her sister the best birthday gift But her mother was worried, She said: "Remember,
go straight to Anna's house,The woods are dangerous, you know, Hans the wolf can snatch
the gift!!"
But when ELsa noticed some lovely flowers in the woods, she forgot her promise to her
mother.
She picked a few flowers and thought she will give it to her sister.
Hans the wolf was hiding behind the trees and watching all this.
ha ha ha I will reach Anna's house and steal all of her gifts... ha ha ha
He took a shortcut...
And reached Anna's home, Anna was not present in her home, He laid in Anna's Bed and took
a quilt on him, his whole face was hidden.
When Elsa reached there he said in Anna's voice:
Hooo Elsa give me my gift.
Anna, What happened to your voice?
Hoooo, I ate a lot of icecream yesterday so i have a bad throat today!
Suddenly she saw a tail hanging from bed, she was shocked, she said
Anna, what is this?
Hooooo....
Who are you?
I am hans the wolf, give this gift to me!!
After saying this he started lauging badly and jumping on the bed.
In the mean time, Anna reached there
she throw her lamp on his face and he was fainted out.
Then she asked Elsa about the whole matter?
Elas's mother reached there and told the whole story, Elsa said sorry to her mother.
My child, Never forget the advice of your parents and in your life you will get two
paths, never get fooled of shortcut, because it can be harmful for you and Anna never leave
your home open because any stranger can get in and it can
be very harmful for all of us!
And then, they celebrated Anna's Birthday.
So kids, tell us which part of the story did you like the most and what did you learnt
from it?
If you have enjoyed this story please like us and subscribe and we will come with another
one.
Good bye!!
